_sText:
A group of terrorists who fulfilled sentence in a prison located
in Minnesota, had been hardly mistreated during 10 years. 
One year later, after they recovered their freedom, some of them come 
back to blow up the prison and all members with it. 
Now it's time to see that revenge is not a joke...

This is my "first" serious map, I began to map in 16 years old but I don't centered me in upload my own map into a page. Is the first time (and not the last) that I upload a map. If I upload this map, is for one reason, that I believe this is my better map in this 7 years in the mapping world.
